<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für Peter Steinberger, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_64" id="32r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_64_r2l1">Der Stat cʒu weiſſemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_64_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Peter Steinberger vnſer Burger / vvie daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l3">Er etwaʒ von ſeiner notdurfft wegen beẏ euch cʒuhandeln hab / darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l4">Er eins ſlehten geleites bey euch wol bedörfft / Vnd das Jm von ew ver - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l5">ſagt ſeẏ worden / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jm durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ein ſlehts geleite </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l6">bey euch / vnd cʒu euch vnd von euch <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l7">notdurfft cʒehandeln vnd auſʒetragen / Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r2l9"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Natiuit<ex>atis</ex></expan> <expan>glo<ex>rio</ex>ſ<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>vırg<ex>inis</ex></expan> <expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_64" id="32r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Weissemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
                        Peter Steinberger, unser burger, wie daz er etwaz von seiner notdurfft wegen
                        bey euch czu handeln hab, darczu er eins slehten geleites bey euch wol
                        bedörfft, und das im von ew versagt sey worden.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ein slehts geleite bey euch und
                        czu euch und von euch <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet,
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein notdurfft cze handeln und
                        auszetragen, als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>nativit<ex>atis</ex></expan>
<expan>glo<ex>rio</ex>s<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>virg<ex>inis</ex></expan>
<expan>M<ex>arie</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
